io.github.nucleuspowered.nucleus.api.service

Interface NucleusSeenService.SeenInformationProvider

  • Enclosing interface:
    NucleusSeenService

    public static interface NucleusSeenService.SeenInformationProvider
    A NucleusSeenService.SeenInformationProvider object can hook into the seen command and provide extra information on a player.

    This must be registered with the NucleusSeenService
